🚗 Bright Motors — Car Sales Analysis 
BrightLearn Data Analytics Case Study | Junior Data Analyst

📌 Overview 
This project is a data analytics case study completed as part of the BrightLearn Data Analytics programme. 
The scenario involves acting as a Junior Data Analyst for Bright Motors, preparing business insights 
for a newly appointed Head of Sales to support strategic decision-making across their dealership network.

🎯 Business Objectives 
Identify which car makes and models generate the most revenue Analyse the relationship between price, mileage, 
and year of manufacture Determine which regions have the highest sales volumes 
Uncover emerging customer purchasing trends Provide recommendations to improve dealership profitability

🛠️ Tools & Tech 
Stack SQL / Processing - Snowflake / MySQL 
Visualisation - Power BI / Excel 
Presentation - PowerPoint / Canva Planning - Miro / Figma
